<div id="start-screen" class="start-screen">
    <div class="main-wrapper">
        <!-- area interactiva izq -->
        <div class="left-panel">
            <div class="brand">
                <h1>MI PORTAFOLIO</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Full Stack & AI Engineer</p>
            </div>
            <button id="btn-start" class="btn-pixel">PRESS START</button>
        </div>

        <!-- separador cadenas -->
        <div class="separator-chains">
            <div class="chain"></div>
            <div class="chain-badge">VS</div>
            <div class="chain"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- area sobre mi -->
        <div class="right-panel">
            <div class="about-me glass-panel">
                <h2>¿Quién soy?</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="about-top">
                        <p>Soy Joaquin Alvarado, un desarrollador apasionado por crear 
                        mundos digitales interactivos. Mi especialidad es el Backend 
                        tanto en Rust como en Python (FastAPI), me enfoco en la arquitectura 
                        limpia y la escalabilidad de mis aplicaciones, además de integrar 
                        Inteligencia Artificial para desarrollar soluciones y mejorar la 
                        experiencia del usuario.</p>
                        <div class="about-image">
                            <img src="/CV_Yo.png" alt="Joaquin Alvarado" class="profile-img" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="extra-info">
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="label">Misión</span>
                            <span class="value">Arquitectura Limpia</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="label">Visión</span>
                            <span class="value">Innovación IA</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    const btn = document.getElementById('btn-start');
    const screen = document.getElementById('start-screen');

    btn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
        screen?.classList.add('fade-out');
        setTimeout(() => {
            if (screen) screen.style.display = 'none';
            document.dispatchEvent(new Event('game-start'));
        }, 1000);
    });
</script>

<style>
    .start-screen {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        background: #000;
        z-index: 9999;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: #fff;
        transition: opacity 1s;
    }

    .main-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        width: 95%;
        max-width: 1250px;
        height: 75%; /* reducido ligeramente */
        align-items: center;
        gap: 40px;
    }

    .start-screen.fade-out {
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* paneles */
    .left-panel {
        flex: 0.7; /* empujado a la izq */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .right-panel {
        flex: 1.3; /* mas espacio para info */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .brand h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        color: #ffd43b;
        text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #8c4e00;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .subtitle {
        color: #4dabf7;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* cadenas separadoras */
    .separator-chains {
        width: 40px;
        height: 70%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 15px;
    }

    .chain {
        flex: 1;
        width: 6px;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(
            #ffd43b 0, #ffd43b 10px,
            #8c4e00 10px, #8c4e00 12px
        );
        border: 2px solid #fff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 212, 59, 0.3);
    }

    .chain-badge {
        background: #fff;
        color: #000;
        padding: 10px;
        border: 4px solid #ffd43b;
        font-weight: bold;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        width: 35px;
        height: 35px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* contenido panel derecho */
    .about-me {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 30px 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 780px; /* contenedor mas ancho */
        margin: 0;
    }

    .about-me h2 {
        color: #ffd43b;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,212,59,0.3);
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .about-me p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #e0e6ed;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .about-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .about-top {
        display: flex;
        gap: 35px;
        align-items: center; /* mejor centrado vertical */
    }

    .about-image {
        width: 250px; /* foto grande */
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .profile-img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: contain;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 3px solid #ffd43b;
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 212, 59, 0.25);
    }

    .extra-info {
        display: flex;
        gap: 40px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .info-item {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 5px;
    }

    .info-item .label {
        color: #4dabf7;
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .info-item .value {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: #fff;
    }

    /* boton */
    .btn-pixel {
        background: #ff6b6b;
        border: 4px solid #fff;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #fff;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #8c0000;
        transition: transform 0.1s, box-shadow 0.1s;
    }

    .btn-pixel:active {
        transform: translate(4px, 4px);
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #8c0000;
    }

    .btn-pixel:hover { background: #ff8787; }

    @keyframes float {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }
</style>
